import React from 'react'; import '../Confirmation.css'; // Import the global styles function BookingConfirmed({ bookingDetails }) { const { name, email, phone, address, postalCode, bookingDate, // Make sure to use the right key for the date timeFrom, timeTo, serviceName, servicePrice, totalArea, discount, amount, } = bookingDetails; // Properly format the date. // Using .toLocaleDateString() might cause issues with different timezones or locale. const formattedDate = bookingDate ? new Date(bookingDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) : 'No Date'; console.log("Booking Date:", bookingDate); // For debugging return (

Booking Confirmed

Thank you for booking with us, {name}!

{/* User Information */}
Name: {name}
Email: {email}
Phone: {phone}
Address: {address}
Postal Code: {postalCode}
{/* Date and Time */}
Date: {formattedDate} {/* Updated to use formattedDate */}
Time Slot: {timeFrom} - {timeTo}
{/* Service Information */}
Service Name: {serviceName}
Service Price (per m²): ${servicePrice}
Total Area (sqm): {totalArea} m²
Discount: {discount}%
Total Amount: ${amount}

We look forward to providing you with excellent service!

); } export default BookingConfirmed;
